# Walkthrough - Navbar and Hero Section Upgrade

I have updated your Landing Page with a modern, animated Navbar and Hero Section.

## Changes

### 1. New Navbar ([Navbar.jsx](file:///d:/project/Skill_Gap%20Analyser%20and%20placement%20intelligence/client/src/components/Navbar.jsx))
- **Modern Design**: Glassmorphism effect on scroll.
- **Responsive**: Mobile drawer menu with smooth transitions.
- **Interactivity**: Dropdown menus for desktop navigation.

### 2. New Hero Section ([HeroSection.jsx](file:///d:/project/Skill_Gap%20Analyser%20and%20placement%20intelligence/client/src/components/HeroSection.jsx))
- **Animated Background**: Gradient orbs and a grid pattern with pulse animations.
- **Animations**: `fade-in`, `slide-up`, and `float` animations for elements.
- **Content**:
    - "New: AI-Powered Skill Gap Analysis" badge.
    - Strong value proposition with gradient text.
    - Animated dashboard mockup with growing charts.

### 3. Styling Updates ([index.css](file:///d:/project/Skill_Gap%20Analyser%20and%20placement%20intelligence/client/src/index.css))
- Added custom Tailwind utility classes for animations (`.animate-fadeIn`, `.animate-slideUp`, `.animate-float`, etc.).

### 4. Integration ([LandingPage.jsx](file:///d:/project/Skill_Gap%20Analyser%20and%20placement%20intelligence/client/src/pages/LandingPage.jsx))
- Replaced the old inline hero section with the new `<HeroSection />`.
- Imported and used the updated `<Navbar />`.

## Verification Results

### Automated Verification
